%p.intro-text
  Welcome to bombvacuum a multilayer mine sweeper variant. You can start playing a signal player game now
  or if you sign in that's where the
  %sapn.highlight
    real magic happens with multilayer games.

%p.outro-text
  See you on the fields! -team

= link_to '/users/auth/facebook', class:'sign-in' do
  %i.icon-facebook-sign
  Sign in and start playing

.reassurance
  Dont worry we wont post anything without your permission. We hate that too. You can always
  = link_to 'sign in with email.', '#', 'data-reveal-id' => 'reg'


#reg.reveal-modal
  .reg-wrap
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        .note.notice= notice
        .note.alert= alert
        %h2 Sign in
      = form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => session_path(resource_name)) do |f|
        = devise_error_messages!
        .row
          .large-12.columns
            = f.email_field :email, :autofocus => true, placeholder:'Email', class:'email-field'
            = f.password_field :password, placeholder:'Password', class:'password-field'
        .row
          .large-6.columns
            .links
              - if devise_mapping.rememberable?
                %div
                  %label
                    = f.check_box :remember_me, style:'width: 11px; height: 14px;}'
                    Please remember my email.
              = render 'devise/shared/links'
          .large-6.columns
            = f.submit 'Sign In', class:'submit-button'

